{"tid":1531324,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"[置頂] [春袋] 機場禁制令嚴重保安漏洞","createTime":"2019-09-02T07:39:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-02T14:00:31.000Z","uid":274475,"like":51,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"4bdc9c523c130fed0e0ed9c6a10e469a39c591d3","tid":1531324,"uid":274475,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T07:39:48.000Z","msg":"工作關係，小妹響出左機場禁制令後都坐左幾次飛機，分享下經驗。<br />\n<br />\n有左機場禁制令，機場保安就可以阻止非旅客進入機場大樓，而保安分辨旅客嘅方法就係響大樓門口檢查每個人兩樣野：1) 護照，2) 當日要坐嘅航班嘅booking confirmation (printed or digital)。<br />\n<br />\n由於長期都有大量人排隊入大樓，所以<span style=\"color: green;\">保安只會好快望一望1+2嘅名同航班時間match唔match，十秒唔到就放你入去</span>。咁大家買過機票都知，航班booking confirmation係買完機票後email send俾你嘅，小妹作為時常要坐飛機嘅人，就好擔心<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">如果有暴徒每次入機場都用舊嘅booking confirmation改左個日期同航班編號做當日是但一班機</span></span>，拎埋passport，要混入機場根本完全防不勝防<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n又或者啲塞路不合作運動暴徒再醒啲，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">個個P張假booking confirmation坐車入機場，身上咩gear都唔拎又著到旅客咁，拎埋個喼，咁警察根本完全冇任何方法分辨到暴徒同旅客</span></strong>，日日有一萬個假旅客坐車出出入入，塞到水洩不通，又同真旅客混埋一齊，警察都唔知打邊個好，成個機場運作咪崩潰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n犯法野千祈唔好做，會令政府個春袋爆煲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b70c6615d8d4d7e8be38c0634374200e88e4d6eb","tid":1531324,"uid":81652,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T07:42:04.000Z","msg":"虛假文書加違反禁制令<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/